# AIDD Shared Directory Synchronization
#
# This file lists directories to sync to all projects at the start of each iteration.
# Rename this file to "copydirs.txt" and add absolute paths (one per line).
#
# Use cases:
# - Sync IDE configuration (.vscode, .windsurf, .claude)
# - Share linting rules across projects
# - Distribute common scripts or templates
# - Keep project guidelines up to date
#
# Format: One absolute path per line
# Lines starting with # are comments and are ignored
# Empty lines are ignored
#
# Examples (uncomment and modify for your environment):
#
# /d/applications/.claude
# /d/applications/.windsurf
# /c/shared/configs
# /home/user/.vscode

